      "parameters": {
        "content": "# MCP (Model Context Protocol) Demo Workflow\n\nThis workflow is designed to explain MCP concepts in a simple way inside n8n.\n\nFlow:\n1. Manual Trigger starts the workflow.\n2. User Query node simulates user input.\n3. MCP Client Concept node explains how MCP communicates.\n4. Tool Response node simulates a response from an MCP Server.\n5. Final Output node formats the result.\n\nYou can use this workflow to explain:\n- MCP Client\n- MCP Server\n- Tools\n- Context Sharing\n- AI Agent Communication"
      },
      "id": "1a20e5a9-14d8-49f0-93b0-11b300d6ec03",
