      "parameters": {
        "content": "## MCP Client Concept\n\nThis node represents the MCP Client.\n\nResponsibilities:\n- Sends requests\n- Uses tools\n- Shares context\n- Communicates with MCP Servers\n\nExample Tool:\nfetch_order_tool"
